Where to Watch

In this special-effects spectacular, the legendary lizard returns to carve a swath of destruction across New York City. Matthew Broderick stars as a biologist who teams with a French investigator (Jean Reno) to stop the rampaging reptilian monster. Maria Pitillo, Hank Azaria, Michael Lerner. Co-written and produced by Dean Devlin and Roland Emmerich.
